relevant_communication:
Events: Annual Farm Visits to demonstrate Integrated Farm Management / Sustainable Agriculture in practice. 
Participation in EIP-Workshop in Croatia 2017, active involvement in CDGs on CAP and Environment & Climate Change, giving various speeches and presentations at European conferencess and workshops, involvement in projects (for example PEGASUS project) etc. 
Publications: 
* Various Topic Sheets on different aspects of Integrated Farm Management; 
* EISA Annual Report 2017; 
* Integrated Farming - A holistic system for sustainable development in European agriculture (brochure); 
etc.,  
publications all available on the EISA website.
